lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur midfielder Mousa Dembele has signed a new contract that will run until 2019, the club said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Dembele Signs New Three-Year Tottenham Contract
headline.main: Dembele Signs New Three-Year Tottenham Contract
